<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml-1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="FR" lang="FR">
<head>
	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
	<meta http-equiv="expires" content="0">
	<meta http-equiv="pragma" content="no-cache">
	<meta http-equiv="cache-control" content="no-cache, must-revalidate">
  <title><%= @html_newsletter.subject %></title>

	<style type="text/css">
		
		body { background-color: #ffffff;	text-align:left; }
		a img { border: none;	}
		table.bg1 { background-color: #ffffff; }
		table.bg2 { background-color: #ffffff; }
		table { text-align:left; }
		td.permission { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 5px 20px 5px 20px; }
		td.permission p { font-family: helvetica,verdana,arial,sans-serif; line-height:1.5em; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal;
		   color: #333333; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
		td.permission p.de { color:#CA001C;	}
		td.permission p a { font-family: helvetica,verdana,arial,sans-serif; line-height:1.5em; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; color: #333333; }
		td.header img {	margin: 10px 0;	}
		td.body { padding: 0 20px 20px 20px; background-color: #ffffff; }
		td.sidebar img { margin:0; padding:0; }
		td.buttons { padding: 20px 0 0 0; }
		td.mainbar h1 { font-family: helvetica,verdana,arial,sans-serif; line-height:1.5em;	font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;
	   	margin: 1em 0 0.6em 0; padding: 0; }
		td.mainbar h1 a { font-family: helvetica,verdana,arial,sans-serif; line-height:1.5em;
	   	font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;	margin: 1em 0 0.6em 0; padding: 0; color: #333333; text-decoration: none; }
		td.mainbar h1 a:hover { color: #3C77B9; }
		td.mainbar h2 { font-family: helvetica,verdana,arial,sans-serif; line-height:1.5em; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #333333; margin: 1em 0 0.6em 0; padding: 0;}
    td.mainbar a {font-family: helvetica,verdana,arial,sans-serif;color: #333333; text-decoration: none;}
    td.mainbar a:hover {color: #3C77B9;}
		td.mainbar h2 a { font-family: helvetica,verdana,arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.5em;font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;
		  color: #333333; text-decoration: none;margin: 1em 0 0.8em 0;padding: 0;}
		td.mainbar h2 a:hover {color: #3C77B9;}
		td.mainbar img.hr { margin: 0;padding: 0 0 10px 0;}
		td.mainbar, td.mainbar p {font-family: helvetica,verdana,arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.5em;
		   font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;color: #333333; margin: 0 0 14px 0; padding: 0;}
		td.mainbar .de, td.mainbar p.de {color:#C6001C;}
		td.mainbar p a {font-family: helvetica,verdana,arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.5em;font-size: 13px;font-weight: normal;color: #3333FF;}
		td.mainbar p.more a { font-family: helvetica,verdana,arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.5em;font-size: 13px;font-weight: normal;color: #3333FF; text-decoration: none;}
		td.mainbar ul { margin: 8px 0 0 20px; padding: 0;}
		td.mainbar ul li {font-family: helvetica,verdana,arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.5em;font-size: 13px;font-weight: normal;color: #333333;margin:8px 0;}
		td.mainbar ul li a, td.mainbar a {font-family: helvetica,verdana,arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.5em;font-size: 13px;font-weight: normal;color: #3C77B9; text-decoration:none;}
		td.mainbar ul li a:hover, td.mainbar a:hover {color: #BF0000; text-decoration:none;}
		td.footer { padding: 0 20px 0 20px; background-image: url('footer-bg.gif'); background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: top center; background-color: #ffffff;height: 61px; vertical-align: middle;}
		td.footer p { font-family: helvetica,verdana,arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.5em;font-size: 11px;font-weight: normal;color: #ffffff; line-height: 16px;margin: 0;padding: 0;}
		td.mainbar p.forum, td.mainbar p.forum a {font-size:10.5px;font-style:italic;}
		.clear {clear:both;line-height:0.1px;}
		tfoot tr td.permission {margin-top: 20px;padding-top: 10px;border-top:solid 1px #AAA;}
	</style>


</head>
<body>
	<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="bg1">
		<tr>
	  	<td align="center">
        <table width="600" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="bg2">
        	<tr>
          	<td class="permission" align="left">
            	<p>Vous n'arrivez pas à lire cet email? <a href="*|ARCHIVE|*">Lisez le dans votre navigateur web</a>.</p>
            </td>
					</tr>
          <tr>
          	<td class="header" align="center">
            	<img src="/images/logo_cf_newsletter.jpg" alt="Connexion Française" width="610" height="100" />
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          	<td valign="top" class="body mainbar">
							<%= yield %>
						</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
					  <td valign="top" class="body mainbar" style="padding-top:10px;">
					    <table width="610" valign="top" class="body mainbar">
              <tr valign="middle">

              <td width="30" align="right"><a href="http://www.connexion-francaise.com/pages/facebook" style="text-decoration:none;"><img src="/images/facebook.png" style="margin-top:3px;"></a></td>
              <td width="3" />
              <td width="222"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/FanFrancoAllemand.DeutschFranzoesischFan?sk=app_235111576516530">rejoignez-nous sur Facebook</a></td>

              <td width="50" align="right"><a href="http://forum.connexion-francaise.com" style="text-decoration:none;"><img src="/images/picto_forum.jpg" style="margin-top:3px;" width="32" height="32"></a></td>
              <td width="3" />
              <td width="202"><a href="http://forum.connexion-francaise.com">participez à nos forums de discussions</a></td>

              </tr>
              <tr valign="middle">
              <td width="30" align="right"><a href="http://twitter.com/connexionfr" style="text-decoration:none;"><img src="/images/twitter.png" style="margin-top:3px;"></a></td>
              <td width="3" />
              <td width="222"><a href="http://twitter.com/connexionfr">suivez-nous sur twitter</a></td>

              <td width="50" align="right"><a href="https://www.xing.com/net/connexionfrancaise" style="text-decoration:none;"><img src="/images/small-xing.jpg" style="margin-top:3px;"></a></td>
              <td width="3" />
              <td width="202"><a href="https://www.xing.com/net/connexionfrancaise">retrouvez-nous sur Xing</a></td>

              </tr>
              </table>
					  </td>
					</tr>
					<tfoot>
					<tr><td>&nbsp;<td></tr>
					<tr>
						<td class="permission" align="left">
								<p>Vous recevez cet email parce que vous êtes inscrit à notre newsletter.</p>
	              <p>Plus intéressé? <a href="*|UNSUB|*">Se désinscrire</a> de cette liste.</p>
             </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              *|LIST:ADDRESS|*
            </td>
          </tr>
					</tfoot>
				</table>
			</td>					
		</tr>
	</table>
</body>
</html>
